title: Multi-agent routing with tiered context bindings
---
Route incoming messages to specialized agents via priority-ordered matching: peer ID > parent peer > guild roles > guild > team > account > channel > default. Config-driven agent bindings list. New routing module; config schema extension. Enables #research → researcher agent, #builds → builder agent without user-side routing.